name: The Gold App UI Kit
description: The Gold App UI Kit is designed with a clean and sleek style that contains 30+ high-quality screens and responsively resize features for iOS & Android, ready to use and ready to kickstart your design process. The Gold App UI Kit is compatible and works smoothly with Figma, Adobe XD & Sketch with well-layered and organized, responsive resize, global color, and text styles. You will get 30+ Screens Design - Figma, XD & Sketch files of the kit. Thank you!
